Class MathematicaBraceMatcher

java.lang.Object
  de.halirutan.mathematica.codeInsight.MathematicaBraceMatcher
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.intellij.lang.PairedBraceMatcher
public class MathematicaBraceMatcher
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.intellij.lang.PairedBraceMatcher

Provides the highlighting of paired braces. This works as follows: When you navigate the cursor near a brace/bracket/parenthesis then its corresponding closing (or opening, if you are over the closing one) brace changes its color, so that you see which portion of the code is embraced.

Author:
patrick (4/2/13)
